Job Title: .NET Developer

Location: Cedar Rapids, IA

Employment Type: full-time

Listed Skills: Engineering, Information Technology

Description:
Job#: 2019543

Job Description:

Apex is seeking a strong .NET Developer local to Iowa for a financial services client. If interested please send your resume to Kristin Pulkrab at [email protected]

NET Developer

Hybrid – Des Moines, IA or Cedar Rapids, IA

This position involves the design & coding new or changes in large financial and billing applications using the required skills. The position will resolve and support production issues that arises from the application. Should have good written and oral communication skills, with can do attitude.

Required Skills:

Production Support experience.NET Core.NET 4Rest APISQL server

Nice to have

Azure cloudService Broker or Messaging queue experience
